## MONOREPO STRUCTURE — READ ALL OF THESE

Start by scanning and reading the following directory tree and understanding each app's role:

```
/apps
  /web-app          → Parent-facing React/Next.js web dashboard
  /desktop-agent    → Electron app that runs silently on the student's Windows PC
  /mobile           → React Native / Expo Android app for student's phone
  /backend          → Node.js / Express (or NestJS) REST API server

/packages
  /shared           → Shared types, constants, utilities used across apps
  /ui               → Shared UI component library (if present)
  /config           → Shared ESLint, TypeScript, environment config

/prisma (or /db)    → Database schema (Prisma ORM or equivalent)
```

